OL,3,CThree people charged with murder after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Coventry
OL,6,FThree people have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder after a man was found dead in
OL,8,FCoventry.
OL,10,FThomas Niven was found in a wheelie
OL,11,Fbin in a park off Daimler Road on
OL,12,FFriday, March 13.
OL,14,FTammy Sturdy, aged 45, Camron Sturdy,
OL,15,Faged 21 and Shane Turkington, aged 37,
OL,16,Fall from Coventry, have been charged
OL,17,Fwith murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
