OL,3,CThree people charged with murder after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Coventry
OL,6,FThey have all been remanded in custody
OL,7,Fand are due to appear at Coventry
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday, March
OL,9,F19.
OL,11,FPolice are continuing to investigate
OL,12,Fand anyone with information, who may
OL,13,Fnot have spoken to them yet is being
OL,14,Fencouraged to get in touch by calling
OL,15,F101, quoting incident number 4148 of
OL,16,F13 March.
OL,18,FPeople can also contact Crimestoppers
OL,19,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111.
